---

Modifications made for HARTOS integration:
- All `from aider.X` imports changed to relative imports
- LiteLLM dependency removed, replaced with hart_model_adapter.py
- Aider's InputOutput class replaced with io_adapter.py (SimpleIO)
- pexpect/psutil removed from run_cmd.py, using stdlib subprocess
- oslex made optional with shlex fallback
- rich made optional with minimal Console stub
